Akabeko is one of the best new restaurants in the neighborhood, offering a delightful fusion of French and Japanese cuisine. The food is delicate, yet incredibly flavorful, and their wine pairing is stellar. The cozy and charming decor adds to the overall experience. A big thank you to the whole team for making my night special.  Make sure to go before they fill up!
